  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个安全模块的流转图。核心是两个节点：Security_Encryption负责加密，Security_IntrusionDetection负责入侵检测。我想让它们形成一个循环——加密后的数据流去检测，检测完再回加密做二次加固。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，循环结构。那方向是加密节点指向检测节点，检测节点再指回加密节点？还是单向的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，双向循环。加密到检测，检测完再回加密。这样表示数据在加密和检测之间流转。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出来：Security_Encryption指向Security_IntrusionDetection，然后Security_IntrusionDetection再指回Security_Encryption。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说的有问题。检测节点指回的时候，终点应该还是Security_Encryption对吧？但我看你画的好像终点也是加密节点，这个是对的。不过让我再确认下——检测节点的标签是Security_IntrusionDetection，不是别的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_IntrusionDetection",
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，检测节点标签是Security_IntrusionDetection，回指到Security_Encryption。两个节点名称都没错。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_IntrusionDetection",
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "布局用从左到右吧，LR方向，这样循环看起来比较直观。加密在左，检测在右，箭头形成一个回环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。从左到右布局：Security_Encryption在左侧，箭头指向右侧的Security_IntrusionDetection，再由检测节点回指到加密节点，形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection"
      ],
